Comment.val:
The Memory table is build in a subtask here, because it has to fill the v.SUM-fields, which MUST be defined in this task in order to be refreshed properly in case of change. They are not refreshed on time, if they are defined in the upper task.
There also the "Find old table line" cannot be started in the upper task, but in this task (after having rebuild the memory table).
